    "translation":{"eng":"One who dives into the waves of the ocean of gaura-prema becomes a confidential associate of Śrī Śrī Rādhā-Mādhava. Whether a person lives in his home as a householder or in the forest as a renunciant, if he exclaims, “Hā Gaurāṅga!” Narottama dāsa begs for his association."}}
